Package: quone
Title: A Typed Functional Language that Compiles to R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("armcn", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "quone@example.com")
Description: Provides an R interface to the Quone compiler, a statically typed
    functional language with Hindley-Milner type inference that compiles to
    idiomatic R code. Includes functions to compile, type-check, format, and
    evaluate Quone source files, as well as an interactive REPL.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/armcn/quone-lang
BugReports: https://github.com/armcn/quone-lang/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
